discovered by legendary producer Evan Rogers while holidaying in the Caribbean. 
The album is a fusion of dancehall, reggae and R&B and manages to capture the
 sunshine feel of the Caribbean Islands. The UK top ten single &#039;Pon De Replay&#039; is 
also included.
